    "body": "Hi there! It looks like you are not setting your provider properly. What you need is a provider for Trezor. We found this from a while back, may be worth taking a look at to see if it helps: https://github.com/daonomic/trezor-web3-provider \r\n\r\nAnother option is to transfer some Ether to a separate mnemonic, if you are just trying to do this once. Sorry you've encountered trouble with this! We'll leave this open as a potential feature request in the future. ",
